detaileddescription.para:
Counter for UHF messages. Is incremented each time after CAN messages is sent to SAM. 
 RAM block is placed in Standby RAM. 
range {0-255u} 
 context {is assigned to locally declared Telegram message counter in evUHFSenden and incremented after message is sent to SAM} 
 protection {static global variable for UHF_Task.c}
